## Hello, Stranger — The Pudding (Alvin Chang)

Source: https://github.com/the-pudding/hello-stranger
Project: https://pudding.cool/2025/06/hello-stranger/

Specific assets adapted from this project:
  - Sprite art (the 36 hand-drawn ASCII character sprites in
    version2/web/sprites.json, used unchanged).
  - Three-tone color-derivation algorithm — the darkenColor,
    lightenColor, and darkestColor functions ported line-for-line
    into version2/web/renderer.js.
  - The color palette hex values inherited into version2/web/colors.json
    (re-organized into a 2D mood × energy grid for our semantics).
  - The CSS <pre> + negative letter-spacing rendering approach used in
    version2/web/styles.css (.asciiContainer block).

