## Adafruit GFX Library

Source: https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit-GFX-Library

A snapshot of this library is checked into version1/Adafruit-GFX-Library-master/
for legacy firmware builds. It is distributed under the BSD license; see that
directory's own license file for the full terms.
